      Distributed Creation Inc., whether by ownership or otherwise; and
      “control” means possessing, directly or indirectly, the power to direct or
      cause the direction of the management, policies or operations of an
      entity, whether through ownership of fifty percent (50%) or more of the
      voting securities, by contract or otherwise.
The categories of personal information disclosed to our Corporate
      Affiliates are those described in the Section of this Privacy Policy
      titled
Personal Information We Collect.
