How to Request and/or Demand
Please see the claim procedure below if you would like to (1) request to
      be informed of a utilization purpose of retained personal data that can
      identify you, (2) request that we disclose to you retained personal data
      that can identify you, (3) request that we make a correction, addition or
      deletion in regard to the contents of retained personal data that can
      identify you, (4) request that we cease utilization of, or delete,
      retained personal data that can identify you, (5) request that we cease a
      third-party provision of retained personal data that can identify you,
      and/or (6) request that we disclose our record on a third-party provision:
Claim Procedure;
